# =============================================================================
# DevFlow — Environment Variables
# =============================================================================
# This project runs entirely locally with IndexedDB (Dexie.js).
# No environment variables are required — just npm install && npm run dev.
#
# If you want to run the Python backup scripts, you can optionally set:
#   SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
#   SUPABASE_KEY=your-service-role-key
# =============================================================================
